title: Ornn mission isnt working?

body:

played 2 games and should have completed 2 of those, but, it isnt showing up

replies.body: According to the [**status page**](http://status.leagueoflegends.com/#na) and updates on the client, there was a short period of time where missions were actually disabled from progressing due to some odd errors. It does look like they've been re-enabled, but there are still a few issues the devs are working out.
Same, got one win with orn on my team, got a update, played one as orn and made sure to do all the quests and it didnt update at all.
